<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.6">
<l>aruḷāta nīraruḷi yavarāvi tuvarāmuṉ</l>
<l>ṉaruḷāḻip puṭkaṭavī ravarvīti yorunāḷeṉ</l>
<l>ṟaruḷāḻi yammāṉaik kaṇṭakkā litucolli</l>
<l>yaruḷāḻi varivaṇṭē yāmumeṉ piḻaittōmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“You who are ungracious be gracious, before her breath dries up,</l>
<l>urge [your] bird with the gracious discus into her street one day!”</l>
<l>When you see the lord with the gracious discus, graciously say</l>
<l>this, bee with round stripes. In what have we failed?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
